{{ 'bakuchiol-price.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<section class="bakuchiol-price page-width">
  <div class="bakuchiol-price__wrapper section-top">
    <div class="bakuchiol-price__image">
      <img src="{{ 'bakuchiol-price.png' | asset_url }}" width="925" height="925" loading="lazy"> 
    </div>

    <div class="bakuchiol-price__content">
      <div class="bakuchiol-price__content-top"> 
        <p class="bakuchiol-price__content-title">FOR ALL SKIN TYPES</p>

        <div class="bakuchiol-price__content-titles">
          <h2>Bakuchiol</h2>
          <h3>Age Delay Serum</h3>
        </div>

        <div class="bakuchiol-price__content-price">
          {% for block in section.blocks %}
            {% if block.settings.product != blank %}
              {% assign product = all_products[block.settings.product] %}

              <span class="product-price">
                {{ product.price | money }}
              </span>

              {% if product.compare_at_price_max > product.price %}
                <span class="product-compare-price">
                  {{ product.compare_at_price_max | money }}
                </span>
              {% endif %}

              <span class="bakuchiol-price__label">25% OFF</span>
            {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bakuchiol-price__content-bottom">
        <div class="bakuchiol-price__content-description">
          <p>
            This clinically inspired bakuchiol serum is powered by 1.0% pure bakuchiol to help soften fine lines, refine texture, and brighten dull, uneven tone—without the harsh dryness of traditional retinoids. The lightweight, cushiony formula layers beautifully under moisturizer or bakuchiol cream, delivering bakuchiol RX–level results with a gentle, skin-loving finish.
          </p>
        </div>

        {% for block in section.blocks %}
          {% if block.type == 'product' and block.settings.product %}
            {% assign product = block.settings.product %}
            <a class="bakuchiol-price-link button-custom button-custom__black" href="{{ product.url }}">
              buy bakuchiol serum now
            </a>
          {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="bakuchiol__section-lable">
    <span></span>
    <p>Results that help reveal your smoothest, brightest skin yet.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="display:none !important; visibility:hidden !important; height:0 !important; overflow:hidden !important;">
  
  <h2>How Often Should I Use Bakuchiol Serum in My Routine?</h2>
  <p>Most people can use bakuchiol serum once daily, either in the morning or evening, depending on how their skin responds. Because bakuchiol is gentler than traditional retinol, many sensitive-skin users find that they can apply bakuchiol every day without flaking or irritation. For those who enjoy a richer texture at night, bakuchiol serum can be layered under a nourishing bakuchiol cream or barrier-repair moisturizer.</p>

  <h2>Can Bakuchiol Cream Replace My Prescription Retinoid or Bakuchiol RX Product?</h2>
  <p>Bakuchiol cream and bakuchiol serum are often chosen as gentler alternatives to prescription retinoids and bakuchiol RX–style treatments. While prescription products may act more aggressively, bakuchiol supports smoother texture, a more even tone, and a firmer look with less risk of peeling or redness. Many users transition from harsh retinoids to a well-formulated bakuchiol serum or bakuchiol cream to maintain results with better comfort.</p>

  <h2>Is Bakuchiol Safe to Use Around the Eyes and Mouth?</h2>
  <p>Bakuchiol is frequently used near delicate areas such as crow’s feet, under-eye fine lines, and smile lines, where traditional retinoids can be too strong. When applied carefully, a bakuchiol serum offers visible smoothing benefits for crepey skin without the stinging or excessive dryness common with stronger actives. If your skin is highly reactive, you can follow bakuchiol with a hydrating eye cream or a lightweight bakuchiol cream for additional comfort.</p>

  <h2>What Ingredients Pair Best With Bakuchiol Serum and Bakuchiol Cream?</h2>
  <p>Bakuchiol works exceptionally well with hydrating and barrier-supporting ingredients such as hyaluronic acid, ceramides, squalane, niacinamide, and peptides. A routine that combines bakuchiol serum, a peptide-rich moisturizer, and sunscreen can help support elasticity and brightness over time. Many modern bakuchiol formulations are designed to mimic bakuchiol RX–style results while remaining compatible with vitamin C, antioxidants, and soothing botanicals.</p>

  <h2>Who Is a Good Candidate for Bakuchiol RX–Level Results Without Irritation?</h2>
  <p>Anyone who wants visibly smoother, brighter, and more even-looking skin but struggles with traditional retinoids is an ideal candidate for bakuchiol serum or bakuchiol cream. Sensitive skin types, those prone to redness, and people with compromised barriers often prefer bakuchiol. With consistent use, a high-quality bakuchiol serum can deliver bakuchiol RX–style benefits—refined pores, softer lines, and improved tone—while respecting the skin’s natural balance.</p>

